Running the K6 Test
You can run this test using the following command:

# Basic run
k6 run k6-parallel-api-test.js

# With environment variables
API_TOKEN=your_token k6 run k6-parallel-api-test.js

# Export results to various formats
k6 run --out json=results.json k6-parallel-api-test.js


Customizing the Test
To adapt this for your specific API:

Update BASE_URL with your API endpoint
Update or add more request groups based on your API endpoints
Modify the payloads to match your API requirements
Adjust the VU counts and test duration for your testing needs
Add more specific checks based on your API response format